  "detailed_description": "<i>WARNING: This video game may potentially trigger seizures for people with photosensitive epilepsy. It also depicts unholy entities tied to some religions and the abduction of a young woman. Player discretion is advised.</i><br><br><i><u>IMPORTANT NOTE: The game focuses on exploration and builds tension by keeping you on your feet, creating a deeper and stressful experience. Its story is unveiled upon investigating your surroundings. Be mindful that it is a difficult game combining investigation, pistol combat, puzzles, jumpscares and being chased.</u></i><br><br>Gnarly Hike is a first-person psychological horror game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/25c2f4e1f8e7723728c8e085b3f9a8f3.poster.avif?t=1706093167\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/25c2f4e1f8e7723728c8e085b3f9a8f3.webm?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/25c2f4e1f8e7723728c8e085b3f9a8f3.mp4?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore an eerie forest in a slow-paced, atmospheric world combining beautiful and horrifying scenery along with the constant fear of being hunted, and enjoy a genuinely terrifying experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Game in a nutshell...</h2><br>The game is set in a forest environment, filled with clues as to what is happening, as well as a Cabin, a Chapel, a Cave, a Hidden Burial Site and a Tower. You will have to investigate all those locations in order to uncover the dark secrets the forest holds, while being hunted by a powerful beast!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Investigate</h2>There are many settings, each with its own variety of details and clues to be uncovered.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/9cf7e62088a62fe1e9cb63d9f2036f3a.poster.avif?t=1706093167\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/9cf7e62088a62fe1e9cb63d9f2036f3a.webm?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/9cf7e62088a62fe1e9cb63d9f2036f3a.mp4?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve puzzles</h2>Like every psychological horror game that takes itself seriously, Gnarly Hike contains multiple puzzles, ranging from easy-peasy-lemon-squeezy to \"Oh my God dude, hurry up, it's coming, the code is ___\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/823c9c0288dee8d1df75f6f1349eacd1.poster.avif?t=1706093167\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/823c9c0288dee8d1df75f6f1349eacd1.webm?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/823c9c0288dee8d1df75f6f1349eacd1.mp4?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perform rituals</h2>This game revolves around the supernatural. Therefore, you will have to perform a number of rituals and spells to make progress in the latter parts of the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/f491d093752bf9f035ccb68ce9633977.poster.avif?t=1706093167\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/f491d093752bf9f035ccb68ce9633977.webm?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/f491d093752bf9f035ccb68ce9633977.mp4?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shoot guns</h2>When spells and rituals don't do the trick, you can always trust your guns to keep the beast at bay long enough for you to escape<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/4d48eb433139bb700754916ca575d2ff.poster.avif?t=1706093167\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/4d48eb433139bb700754916ca575d2ff.webm?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/4d48eb433139bb700754916ca575d2ff.mp4?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Run and Hide</h2>Sometimes, guns and spells just don't do the job...so if nothing else works, maybe it's better to just avoid the beast!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/d05bf95d861949597489efc8db58ecc1.poster.avif?t=1706093167\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/d05bf95d861949597489efc8db58ecc1.webm?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666390/extras/d05bf95d861949597489efc8db58ecc1.mp4?t=1706093167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i><u>...and stay alive!</u></i></strong>",
